<subSubSection lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="12" pageId="10" pageNumber="0" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="10.[816,1452,1515,1903]" lastBlockId="11.[136,771,661,717]" lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="12" pageId="10" pageNumber="0">
Ostiole closer to metacoxal cavity than to lateral margin of metapleuron (
<figureCitation box="[969,1061,1548,1571]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[136,169,573,593]" captionTargetBox="[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 18 External scent efferent system of Polytes lineolatus. a Meso- and metapleuron. b Peritreme. c Detail of evaporatorium. d Spiracular filter system. Bars a 500 µm; b 100 µm; c, d 20 µm" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3636793" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3636793/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="0">Fig. 18a</figureCitation>
); ostiole round, oriented ventrolaterally, visible in lateral view; lateral and posterior margins of ostiolar plate elevated; peritreme obsolete (
<figureCitation box="[1344,1438,1615,1638]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[136,169,573,593]" captionTargetBox="[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 18 External scent efferent system of Polytes lineolatus. a Meso- and metapleuron. b Peritreme. c Detail of evaporatorium. d Spiracular filter system. Bars a 500 µm; b 100 µm; c, d 20 µm" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3636793" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3636793/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="0">Fig. 18b</figureCitation>
), median furrow obsolete. Evaporatorium well developed on meso- and metapleuron; on metapleuron, evaporatorium completely covering ostiolar plate and reaching between coxal cavities, outermargin of metapleural evaporatorium convex; on mesopleuron, well developed on mesepimeron; evaporatorium with minute sensilla (
<figureCitation box="[1221,1313,1814,1837]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[136,169,573,593]" captionTargetBox="[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 18 External scent efferent system of Polytes lineolatus. a Meso- and metapleuron. b Peritreme. c Detail of evaporatorium. d Spiracular filter system. Bars a 500 µm; b 100 µm; c, d 20 µm" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3636793" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3636793/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="0">Fig. 18c</figureCitation>
); mushroom bodies irregular, alveoli with several trabeculae. Metathoracic spiracle wide; metapleural margin of spiracle with several setae; processes of the filter system of irregular diameter, processes spiny (
<figureCitation box="[431,525,694,717]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[136,169,573,593]" captionTargetBox="[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[227,1361,158,541]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 18 External scent efferent system of Polytes lineolatus. a Meso- and metapleuron. b Peritreme. c Detail of evaporatorium. d Spiracular filter system. Bars a 500 µm; b 100 µm; c, d 20 µm" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3636793" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3636793/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Fig. 18d</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
